---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
    title="Men's Midlife Coaching: Navigating Life Transitions | Tom Jameson"
    description="Navigate midlife transitions with confidence through professional men's coaching that addresses career changes, relationship shifts, and personal fulfillment."
    canonical="https://tomcoaching.com/blog/mens-midlife-coaching"
>
    <div class="blog-post-container">
        <div class="container">
            <nav class="breadcrumb">
                <a href="/">Home</a> / <a href="/blog">Blog</a> / Men's Midlife Coaching
            </nav>

            <article class="blog-post">
                <header class="post-header">
                    <div class="post-meta">
                        <span class="category">Midlife</span>
                        <span class="date">December 19, 2024</span>
                    </div>
                    <h1>Men's Midlife Coaching: Navigating Life Transitions</h1>
                    <p class="post-excerpt">Navigate midlife transitions with confidence through professional men's coaching that addresses career changes, relationship shifts, and personal fulfillment.</p>
                </header>

                <div class="post-content">
                    <p>Midlife represents a significant period of transition for many men, often bringing questions about purpose, career satisfaction, and personal fulfillment. Men's midlife coaching provides essential support during this challenging yet transformative period, helping clients navigate changes with confidence and clarity.</p>

                    <p>Professional midlife coaching addresses the unique challenges men face during this stage, including career transitions, relationship changes, health concerns, and the search for deeper meaning and purpose. Coaches work with clients to identify their values, reassess their goals, and create actionable plans for the next chapter of their lives.</p>

                    <p>Effective midlife coaching includes developing strategies for managing stress and anxiety, improving work-life balance, strengthening relationships, and exploring new opportunities for personal and professional growth. Coaches help clients embrace change as an opportunity for renewal rather than a crisis to be feared.</p>

                    <p>Whether you're experiencing a career change, relationship transition, or simply feeling uncertain about your direction, men's midlife coaching can provide the guidance and support you need to navigate this important life stage with confidence and create a fulfilling future.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="related-articles">
                    <h3>Related Articles</h3>
                    <div class="related-grid">
                        <a href="/blog/mens-career-coaching" class="related-card">
                            <h4>Men's Career Coaching: Breaking Through Professional Barriers</h4>
                            <p>Learn how career coaching can help you advance professionally.</p>
                        </a>
                        <a href="/blog/mens-leadership-coaching" class="related-card">
                            <h4>Men's Leadership Coaching: Developing Executive Presence</h4>
                            <p>Build executive presence and leadership skills.</p>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="post-cta">
                    <h3>Ready to Navigate Your Midlife Transition?</h3>
                    <p>Take the first step towards creating a fulfilling next chapter with professional coaching support.</p>
                    <a href="/#contact" class="btn">Book Your Consultation Today</a>
                </div>
            </article>
        </div>
    </div>

    <style>
        .blog-post-container {
            min-height: 100vh;
            background: white;
            padding: 80px 0;
        }

        .breadcrumb {
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: #666;
        }

        .breadcrumb a {
            color: #d0c39b;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .breadcrumb a:hover {
            color: #172a22;
        }

        .blog-post {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: white;
            padding: 3rem;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }

        .post-header {
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .post-meta {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        .category {
            background: #d0c39b;
            color: #172a22;
            padding: 0.3rem 0.8rem;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .date {
            color: #666;
        }

        .post-header h1 {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            color: #172a22;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            line-height: 1.2;
        }

        .post-excerpt {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: #666;
            font-style: italic;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .post-content {
            line-height: 1.8;
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
        }

        .post-content p {
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }

        .related-articles {
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
            padding-top: 2rem;
            border-top: 1px solid #e9ecef;
        }

        .related-articles h3 {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            color: #172a22;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        .related-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 1.5rem;
        }

        .related-card {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            border-radius: 8px;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
            border: 1px solid #e9ecef;
        }

        .related-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }

        .related-card h4 {
            color: #172a22;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }

        .related-card p {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .post-cta {
            text-align: center;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #172a22 0%, #1e3a2e 100%);
            color: #d0c39b;
            padding: 2.5rem;
            border-radius: 12px;
        }

        .post-cta h3 {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .post-cta p {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }

        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #d0c39b;
            color: #172a22;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(208, 195, 155, 0.3);
        }

        .btn:hover {
            background-color: #c4b082;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(208, 195, 155, 0.4);
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .blog-post {
                padding: 2rem;
                margin: 0 1rem;
            }
            
            .post-header h1 {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }
            
            .post-meta {
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 0.5rem;
            }
        }
    </style>

